reviews.review_text: Persian nights in NJ Don't let the setlist fool you. This is a great performance, with Jerry in top form. I think this recording is the best of the available auds on this site. Even Throwing Stones>NFA is fantastic, with the band really seeming to *enjoy* playing that tired combo. And as others have said, the Stranger is one of the best ever.
